In a recent survey, Orick asked participants:
“if you were at a restaurant, which critter

00:00:33.219 --> 00:00:34.640
would make you drop your fork?

00:00:34.640 --> 00:00:35.640
Rodents?

00:00:35.640 --> 00:00:36.640
Cockroaches?

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:37.640
Flies?

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:38.640
Ants?

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:39.640
